cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is about developing a response selection model for goal-oriented dialog systems. It uses neural networks for context modeling and response selection. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as these sub-categories are also relevant to the topic of the paper.
